com.pipe42.data.pojos

Class Owner

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pipe42.data.pojos.Owner

  • public final class Owner
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the Owner model object used in the DAO. It defines the owner/manager and/or the organisation that is responsible for this particular project.
    Since:
    0.1.0
